quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,46,"Por ekzempl, ni send Moses our proofs Pharaoh li elders proklam mi est messenger Lord univers"
  43,47,When li montr them our proofs ili rid them
  43,48,Cxiu sign ni montr them est grand than 1 antaux gxi. Ni aflikt them pest perhaps ili pent
  43,49,(Ili dir O vi magician implore your Lord our behalf relieve this pest) ekde vi hav agreement Him; ni tiam direkt
  43,50,Sed as baldaux as ni relieved their affliction ili reverted
  43,51,Pharaoh anonc al his popol O my popol mi ne posed kingship Egypt these flu river aparten al me Vi ne seg
  43,52,Which unu est put; me ke 1 lowly can est hardly parol
  43,53,Kiel ven li ne posed trezor or; kiel ven angxel ne akompan him
  43,54,Li tiel mistifik his popol ili obe him; ili est wicked popol
  43,55,When ili persist en opposing us ni pun them dron them all
  43,56,Ni rendered them precedent ekzempl others